<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Filter Soccer Players</title>
  <style>
    input { padding: 8px; font-size: 16px; }
    body { background-color: yellow; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h3>Premier League Soccer Players:</h3>
    <p>The form below will enable you to see all of the Premier League soccer players with the entered number of goals as a threshold. Data is retrieved from the Fantasy Premier League API. (You can only use the form once, to use it again you have to restart the app)</p>
  <form action="/filter-players" method="POST">
    <label for="goalThreshold">Minimum Goals:</label>
    <input type="number" id="goalThreshold" name="goalThreshold" placeholder="Enter number of goals" required>
    <button type="submit">Filter Players</button>
  </form>
</body>
</html>